            "body": "Thanks for reply, [~tangzhankun].\nIt's a typo, memory should be 1 GB left.\n\nI cannot share raw SLS configuration since it is generated directly from a production cluster (with 2500 nodes), by tracking all applications submitted on that day, including Spark, MapReduce and other frameworks. ",
